dct_description_sm: This long folded map depicts Monmouth County and Ocean County shores. The map also lists bodies of water, some land forms, and man-made features, including what look like property lot lines. Latitude and longitude lines are visible. It is undated but likely from the 19th century. There is much foxing, and one piece is torn from the edge.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
No indication to attribute responsibility for this map.
